This provides an entry platform for entering Shipyard items quickly and easily.


Usage:
<pre>
{{ShipyardItem|Name|Size|Volume|Cost}}
</pre>


#Name = x3Wiki compatible Factory or ship... do not enter race names before item.
#Size = Size of Factory S, M, L, XL (leave blank if no size)
#Volume = leave blank if ship, volume of factory.
#Cost = cost of ship or factory. (Use commas)


Test:
<pre>
{{ShipyardItem|Silicon Mine|L|14250|51,160,024}}
</pre>
